      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>in a medium bowl with the<strong> chopped radish </strong>and<strong> cucumber </strong>– this is your <strong>quick-pickled veg</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone</p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the avocado flesh and slice finely lengthways</p>",
