      "instruction": "<p>Once the sweet potato is cooked through, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, then return the tray[s] to the oven and cook for a further 2-3 min – this is your <strong>sesame sweet potato</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>miso paste</strong> in a bowl with a small splash of <strong>pickling</strong> <strong>liquid</strong> from the quick-pickled veg<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>miso mayo</strong></p>",
